{(day) => ( )} {(week) => ( {(value) => ( )} )}
{day().narrow}
{value().day}

{(months) => ( {(month) => ( )} )}
{month().label}
{/* Year View */}
{api().getDecade().start} - {api().getDecade().end}
{(years) => ( {(year) => ( )} )}
{year().label}
) } ```
